    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable project car or budget-friendly commuter. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few small stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires and a brake service to be in top shape. It's a solid, honest car for someone looking for a deal and willing to put in a little work.",
