    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an exceptionally preserved 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. This S54-powered icon features a high-revving 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained double VANOS system, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, mechanical shifts, while the factory limited-slip differential provides superb lateral traction. Crucially, this chassis has received comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full cooling system overhaul. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, free of oxidation or micro-marring, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel. A true collector-grade specimen for the purist who demands mechanical transparency and analog precision.",
